description.fr: {WorldZone:36[Albuera]} est menacée par une invasion Shushu. {CharacterName:474} décide de s'y rendre afin de prêter main forte à {CharacterName:265}. Peut-être trouvera-t-elle de nouveaux indices en chemin.
description.en: {WorldZone:36[Albuera]} is under threat of a Shushu invasion. {CharacterName:474} has decided to go there to help {CharacterName:265}. Maybe she'll find new clues along the way.
description.es: {WorldZone:36[Albuera]} está amenazada por una invasión de fab'huritus. {CharacterName:474} decide ir allí para echar una mano a {CharacterName:265}. Quizás encuentre nuevas pistas por el camino.
description.de: {WorldZone:36[Albuera]} wird von einer Shushu-Invasion bedroht. {CharacterName:474} beschließt, dorthin zu gehen, um {CharacterName:265} zur Hand zu gehen. Vielleicht findet sie unterwegs ja neue Hinweise.
description.pt: {WorldZone:36[Albuera]} está ameaçada por uma invasão Shushu. {CharacterName:474} decide ir até lá para ajudar {CharacterName:265}. Talvez ela encontre novas pistas pelo caminho.

descriptionFinished.fr: Aux prises avec l'envahisseur Shushu venu grignoter le Wakfu de la Barrière de Corail, {CharacterName:265} n'a aucune information à fournir concernant la {Summoning:1354}. Déçue, {CharacterName:474} vous demande de retourner dans les galeries.
descriptionFinished.en: Struggling with the invading Shushus come to nibble the Wakfu from the Coral Reef, {CharacterName:265} has no information to share about the {Summoning:1354}. Disappointed, {CharacterName:474} has asked you to go back to the tunnels.
descriptionFinished.es: En lucha contra los invasores fab'huritus que han venido a mordisquear el Wakfu de la Barrera de Coral, {CharacterName:265} no tiene información que proporcionar sobre la {Summoning:1354}. Decepcionada, {CharacterName:474} le pide que vuelva a las galerías.
descriptionFinished.de: Im Kampf gegen die Shushu-Invasoren, die am Wakfu der Korallenbarriere knabberten, hat {CharacterName:265} keine Informationen in Bezug auf die {Summoning:1354}. Enttäuscht bittet dich {CharacterName:474}, in die Tunnel zurückzukehren.
descriptionFinished.pt: Do encontro com o invasor Shushu que veio devorar o Wakfu da Barreira de Coral, {CharacterName:265} não conseguiu tirar nenhuma informação sobre a {Summoning:1354}. Decepcionada, {CharacterName:474} pede que você volte para as galerias.
